Source.Name: python-poetry-core
Source.Summary: Poetry PEP 517 Build Backend & Core Utilities
Source.Description: A PEP 517 build backend implementation developed for Poetry. This project is intended to be a lightweight, fully compliant, self-contained package allowing PEP 517-compatible build frontends to build Poetry-managed projects.
